---
title: Steaks and Herb Butter with Creamy Mash and Maple-Dijon Bacon Green Beans
description: Tonight's steaks are smothered in herb butter for a sumptuous flavour boost, but it doesn't end there! The mash gets an extra creamy treatment from butter, milk and cream cheese, and the green beans are taken to a whole new level with bacon and a maple-Dijon sauce. This is a meal worthy of serving to your Valentine!
